videos.description: Cameron Johnson and Kenny Williams start out hot from downtown for the Tar Heels on senior day.
videos.headline: UNC's Williams and Johnson knock down 3-pointers early

videos.description: Ebuka Izundu finds the bucket on three-straight possessions as Miami takes the lead over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Izundu sparks Miami scoring on three-straight possessions

videos.description: Dewan Huell picks up the errant Joel Berry pass and slams it home as Miami is out in front of North Carolina.
videos.headline: Miami's Huell turns defense into dunk

videos.description: Luke Maye knocks down a 3-pointer from deep as North Carolina gets back into the game with run.
videos.headline: Maye rattles home 3-pointer to cap UNC 8-0 run

videos.description: Chris Lykes dribbles through two defenders and then knocks down a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Lykes splits defenders and buries a triple

videos.description: Dewan Huell rejects Luke Maye and is rewarded with a bucket on the offensive end for Miami.
videos.headline: Huell pins Maye off the backboard and scores on other end

videos.description: Joel Berry II makes it a one-possession game late after knocking down a 3-pointer for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Berry hits clutch 3-pointer

videos.description: Ja'Quan Newton hits a buzzer-beater after Joel Berry II ties the game as Miami stuns No. 9 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Miami sinks UNC on Newton's buzzer-beater

videos.description: Ja'Quan Newton hits a buzzer-beater after Joel Berry II ties the game as Miami snaps North Carolina's six-game winning streak.
